I really wanted to shoot with her, and eventually mustered up the courage to ask. She turned out to be a really nice girl, and ended up being super patient. It was cold as heck outside, and she took this winter shoot like a champ. I took this picture from the outside of a coffee shop looking in, because I often feel like such an outsider. (Plus, I love the texture windows give).
